This example shows the simple use of XSI shared memory.

Usage
1.server start and wait to receive.
$serv
2.client sent to server and exist.
$client
server will receive client data and exist.

Note
as XSI IPC resource is system resource, it is not released if process don't release it before exit.
we can use ipc tools to see and manage ipc resources.
see man page of "ipcs ipcmk iprm" for more information.
